               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Daily Office Prayers and Litanies (fols. 1ra-16ra)
 II) Śǝrʿāta
                     qǝddāse “Ordinary of the Mass” (fols. 16ra-27vb; 30ra-32vb; 37ra-40vb;
                     42ra-vb)
 III) Anaphoras (fols. 28ra-29vb; 33ra-36vb; 43ra-121vb)
                     III-1) Anaphora of St Epiphanius of Cyprus (fols. 28ra-29vb; 47ra-vb;
                     48va-51vb; 52ra-63rb)
 III-2) Anaphora of Our Lady by St Cyriacus of
                     Behnesa (fols. 63rb-77ra)
 III-3) Anaphora of the 318 Orthodox Fathers of
                     Nicaea (fols. 77ra-88va)
 III-4) Anaphora of St Jacob of Serug (fols.
                     88vb-97rb)
 III-5) Anaphora of St John Chrysostom (fols. 97rb-115va)
                     III-6) Anaphora of St Cyril of Alexandria (fols. 115va-121vb)
 III-7)
                     Anaphora of St Gregory (“Hosanna-liturgy of St Gregory”) (fols. 33ra-va),
                     incomplete
 III-8) Anaphora of St Basil of Caesarea (fols. 33va-36vb;
                     43ra-46vb), incomplete (?)
 
 Additiones 1-5.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>Missal</title>
                  </msItem>
               
               </msContents>
