                        <condition key="deficient">The back board and the most part of the leather
                           cover are missing. Many fols. are missing. Only eight Anaphoras are
                           present, two of them in part. <locus from="28" to="29">28-29</locus>,
                           37-42 have been removed from their respective quires and misplaced.
                              <locus target="#47">47</locus>, 48, 52, 53 are also misplaced. The
                           texts in this part of the Ms. have been delimited tentatively.
                              <locus target="#48">48</locus>, 49, 63 are seriously damaged, part of
                           the text in these folios is lost. <locus target="#46">46</locus> has
                           three holes with insignificant losses of text. Many fols. are worn, the
                           text has been abraded. Some leaves are damaged by humidity.</condition>
