                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#121vb">f. 121vb</locus>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote">: Ownership note.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ ስምዖን።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">This book is of ʾabuna Walda
                              Sǝmʿon.</q>
                           
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus from="122ra" to="123ra">ff. 122ra-123ra l. 7</locus>
                           <desc type="PoemSalam">Unidentified salām-hymn in praise of God, incomplete. </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <note> Incomplete, beginning missing. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus from="123ra7" to="123rb2">f. 123ra, l.7-rb, l.2</locus>
                           <desc type="PoemQene"><term key="Qene" ana="#Qene"/> Qǝne-poem (of the type <term key="EtanaMogar" ana="#EtanaMogar">ʿǝṭāna mogar</term>?).</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"> ዕጣነ፡ ሞገር፡ ግዕዝ። ለእመ፡
                              ብንያም፡ ወዮሴፍ። አዕይንቲሃ፡ ኮከብ፡ በመዝአረ፡ ገጻ፡ ዘአሶንያ፡ መልአከ፡ ሞት፡ ጸዋግ፡ ዘአደመነ፡ ላህያ፡
                              ዘምድረ፡ ሎዛ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ በስዋስወ፡ ወርቅ፡ ዘርእያ፡ ተብሲለ፡ ኃዘን፡ ለነፍሱ፡ {ሲሳያ፡} በይነ፡ ተፈልጦታ፡
                              እምኔነ፡ ይእዜ፡ ለወለተ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ እንዘ፡ ንብል፡ ንላሁ፡ ከመ፡ እምአምላከ፡ ማርያ፡ እምንስት፡
                              ይቲ፡ ሙአግያ፡ እምንስትይቲ፡ ሙኪርያ።</q>
                           
                           <note> The line እምንስትይቲ፡ ሙኪርያ። appears to be a correction for the
                              previous line (እምንስት፡ ይቲ፡ ሙአግያ፡). </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#123rb">f. 123rb</locus>
                           <desc type="Unclear">: Note (a recipe?).</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="am"/>
                           
                           <note> In Amharic. Crudely written, of unclear content. The note contains
                              a number of plant names. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus target="#123v">f. 123va-vb</locus>
                           <desc type="GuestText">Fragment of an unidentified liturgical text.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <note> Some parts of the text poorly visible. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1"><desc>- <locus target="#16v">16v</locus>, 24r, 27r, 27v (in the
                           upper margin): Crude notes.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e2"><desc> <locus target="#122v">122v</locus> (in
                           the bottom margin): Crude note (pen trial?).</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e3"><desc> <locus target="#123r">123r</locus> (in the bottom margin): Crude note in Amharic containing
                           a date: Gǝnbot 7, 54 Year of Mercy (probably 1954 A.M.).</desc></item>
